  "description" : "[img]https://i.imgur.com/p1sbNRX.png[/img]\n[url=https://discord.gg/pS943gDzcU][img]https://i.imgur.com/jbHECqk.png[/img][/url]\n[url=https://www.patreon.com/sleepySva][img]https://i.imgur.com/iGFzaRO.png[/img][/url]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/CmXuZTg.png[/img]\n\n\n[h1]Update v1.4.2, Elegy of The Nightfaeries[/h1]\n\nThis update adds a new insectoid race, the [b]Spectwing[/b], new [b]factory machines[/b], as well the [b]Spectwing Nest[/b], [b]Abyssal Woods[/b] biome, and more!\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/i9o2ONV.png[/img]\n\n\n[h2]Highlights:[/h2]\n\nAdded a new playable race, the [b]Spectwing[/b].\n\nThe Spectwings are a race of winged insectoids, brought into physical form by cosmic rifts known as the Abyss. As natural abyssborn predators, they bear sharp claws, sturdy carapaces, as well as dazzling wings to attract prey.\n\nAdded [b]Scythes[/b], a new weapon type that has lifesteal or inflicts certain unique statuses, but has a weaker damage output compared to other weapons.\n\nAdded a new environment, the [b]Abyssal Woods[/b], replacing the main biome in Desolate planets.\nAdded a new village, the [b]Spectwing Nest[/b], found primarily in Abyssal Woods or Illuminated planets.\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/3u5V8lg.png[/img]\n\n\n⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯\n\nAdditions:\n\nAdded the following tenant types:\n- Luye Heishe (Luye Tag)\n- Seeker (Aurea Tag)\n- Arcanian Starfarer (Astral Tag)\n- Arcanian Mage (Runic Tag)\n\nAdded the following farmables:\n- Fluxroot (Superstorm Expanse, Neon Sea, Viridescent)\n- Tidenut (Shining Sea, Azure Sea)\n- Virusac (Viridescent, Evoaquatic)\n- Bloody Gem (Animus)\n- Jungle Mango (Verdant)\n- Tatalot (Desolate, Nightmist)\n- Shellfruit (Bamboo Forest, Arcane Forest, various undergrounds)\n\nAdded the following factory machines:\n- [b]Refinery[/b]: An industrial machine for turning substances into refined materials and compounds, useful for producing fuel cells, synthweaves and plastic.\n- [b]Fuel Generator[/b]: A standard generator, useful for powering a large quantity of factory machines. Requires refined fuel cells to run.\n\n\n- Added Winter Feast foods! A big thanks to the contributors!\n- Added the Hall of Champions, a small area displaying statues of event contest winners within Lighthaven.\n- Added the Triple Decking Slam.\n- Added Corrodium Dagger, a weapon that inflicts Acidic Burning, which deals Poison damage based on target's maximum health (30 ~ 200 Poison damage per second).\n- Added new colors to the paint station.\n- Added new Titancorp crates.\n- Added a new boss theme, The Living Shadows, by Doranarasi\n- Added a new biome theme, Decline Region, by Doranarasi\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/qkK26zT.gif[/img]\n\n⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯\n\nChanges:\n(Visit the [url=https://github.com/sleepySva/sva_arcana/releases/tag/v1.4.2.0]Arcana Github[/url] for a detailed list of changes)\n  \n⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/LWKTcGv.png[/img]\n\n\nVisit our Discord or the Github page for a more comprehensive changelog about all the other additions and changes!\nHappy Exploring!\n\n\n\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/CmXuZTg.png[/img]\n\n\n\n\n\n\n[h1]Arcana, a Mystical Universe[/h1]\n\nArcana is a growing techno-magic themed Starbound mod that features a vast amount of added content, including:\n\n[list]\n[*]28+ new planets\n\n[*]120+ custom weapons\n\n[*]100+ armor pieces and cosmetics\n\n[*]600+ new tiles and objects\n[/list]\n\nArcana is also constantly updating with new contents, aiming to always provide new magical elements for the star explorers to find.\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/CmXuZTg.png[/img]\n\n\n[h1]New Bosses & Monsters[/h1]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/QuJiMjr.png[/img]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/CmXuZTg.png[/img]\n\n\n[h1]An Abundance of New Content[/h1]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/y4HA0Fb.png[/img]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/Z8cDBAw.png[/img]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/EDOWj5N.png[/img]\n\n[img]https://i.imgur.com/CmXuZTg.png[/img]\n\n\n[h1]New Encounters and Races![/h1]\